  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and ginger, sauté until fragrant.",
    "Stir in chopped carrots and bell pepper, cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add zucchini and stir for another 3 minutes.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth, bring to a boil, then reduce heat.",
    "Add orange zest and orange juice, season with berbere, salt, and pepper.",
    "Simmer uncovered for 15 minutes until vegetables are tender.",
    "Stir in honey and lemon juice, adjust seasoning if needed.",
    "Remove pot from heat and let the stew sit for 5 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, optionally garnish with fresh herbs."
